-Mdz-4oeSX-cQ6Zg4xT3.text: Firefighters have received an unconfirmed report of a house fire.

-Mdz0G467uCJ302_4nAU.text: Firefighters have arrived on site and have confirmed that a two-story house is fully engulfed in flames.

-Mdz10Nw4aGbAJiCKk42.text: Firefighters have initiated a quick search of the premises. They also report that most of the visible fire is on the first floor.

-Mdz22l12KaFz3GUuJ9k.text: Firefighters have entered the house and are searching for occupant who may still be in the house.

-Mdz2Y0j8ASrOLVqlZ8u.text: Firefighters are searching through the second floor as well.

-Mdz2pdqopvK9KG3tTY9.text: Firefighters have extinguished most of the fire on the exterior of the house.

-Mdz3K4HBHFjY_RHgLp9.text: Firefighters have initiated a secondary search of the premises.

-Mdz3k6_R-V6QDrImVxJ.text: Firefighters have confirmed no fire in the basement of the house. Most of the visible fire has been extinguished.

-Mdz455v1H0GGnFSR6mu.text: A report from firefighter on site stated that the second floor is clear of any possible injured occupants.

-Mdz4I0HwAOLRPNdb3V2.text: Citizen user aamanzke's video shows firefighters on site.

-Mdz5-zj9DaAvWayJtYa.text: Firefighters have confirmed that most of the fire has been extinguished with no possible spread of the fire. They have also completed a secondary search of the basement with no injuries reported.

-Mdz5W0nGsoNsP2h22Fb.text: Firefighters are now focusing on the back side of the house. Firefighters have completed the secondary search on the second floor. No injuries were reported.

-Mdz66gI5S2NpqmkA6Rx.text: Firefighters are preparing to clear the house of some debris to gain access to the remaining smoldering spots.

-MdzBQoUL4rc9ocfpvCH.text: Firefighters have completely extinguished the fire. They are performing a final search of the premises.

-MdzE89foLyOqo_EAYLt.text: Firefighters have completed the final search with no remaining fire or smoke.
